{"tid":1018752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗單程證問題 中國各大城市人口爭相嚟香港私家醫院醫療旅遊","createTime":"2019-02-12T12:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T11:00:12.000Z","uid":47359,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"74eb50271c07caa09fea190738e42f741f5ae461","tid":1018752,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:52:37.000Z","msg":"除咗每日150中國移民<br />\n中國各大城市人口爭相嚟香港私家醫院醫療旅遊<br />\n上海、北京、四川、澳門、廣州<br />\n做開港豬嘅中產或有錢人因住收尾幾年<br />\n有咩大病都未及時醫到<br />\n香港人有錢都未必及時入到低/免地價嘅私家醫院<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咩話？<br />\n冇錯政府係用低地價免地價讓塊地畀私家醫院<br />\n<br />\nSource審計署<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.aud.gov.hk/pdf_ca/c59ch04sum.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aud.gov.hk%2Fpdf_ca%2Fc59ch04sum.pdf&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIuvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=a18ac1d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.aud.gov.hk/pdf_ca/c59ch04sum.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n而私家醫院嘅醫護又係由公立醫院用高少少人工搶過嚟<br />\n政府用公帑培訓出身嘅醫護就流失去呢啲私家醫院<br />\n連登仔最關心嘅血，基於人道關係冇可能分公私家分配啦<br />\n<br />\n醫療負荷比你想像中重<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c1d1b28ad565c6285914c636170c496d729dbe","tid":1018752,"uid":47359,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:55:23.000Z","msg":"所以醫療旅遊嘅中國人都有份間接搶走公立醫院人手資源"},{"pid":"bfe1c18cab2347c252bf0a742c9c5f9b4f2cf4e3","tid":1018752,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:58:27.000Z","msg":"旅遊業係香港四大支柱之一 <br />\n<br />\n想搞死香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b92330d601bc18db8088540c42a5d87257b66e","tid":1018752,"uid":37874,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:01:33.000Z","msg":"正常政府應該會睇番究竟 D私家醫院係咪符合&quot;低/免地價&quot;條件<br />\n你專做大陸人生意既話 係咪要政府幫你埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(錢你又搵左 醫生你又搶埋 稅交埋都唔夠正常地價)<br />\n<br />\n不過香港政府係點 大家明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇大陸頭既姐 鬼理你香港人咩"},{"pid":"1e672a7855cb704875087e3671d86eb3003dcfbb","tid":1018752,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bfe1c18cab2347c252bf0a742c9c5f9b4f2cf4e3","tid":1018752,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:58:27.000Z","msg":"旅遊業係香港四大支柱之一 <br />\n<br />\n想搞死香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:01:35.000Z","msg":"為咗賺錢健康都可以俾中國人優先<br />\n你做開狗食開屎？<br />\n97前冇呢個問題香港人都冇死"},{"pid":"602457ee24b8aeeea9c5b88e86e42312ad8c36a3","tid":1018752,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2b92330d601bc18db8088540c42a5d87257b66e","tid":1018752,"uid":37874,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:01:33.000Z","msg":"正常政府應該會睇番究竟 D私家醫院係咪符合&quot;低/免地價&quot;條件<br />\n你專做大陸人生意既話 係咪要政府幫你埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(錢你又搵左 醫生你又搶埋 稅交埋都唔夠正常地價)<br />\n<br />\n不過香港政府係點 大家明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇大陸頭既姐 鬼理你香港人咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"假設政府為香港人著想<br />\n可惜假設fail<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17443a04f3b8fa622749cde6a92c5a4b9a733f59","tid":1018752,"uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:09:30.000Z","msg":"私院已經比大陸狗玩到做手術都要排隊<br />\n97前你比到私院價好快到你"},{"pid":"ad75f5aa41bb38a0e8f2f891202ea9ca8505bb7e","tid":1018752,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17443a04f3b8fa622749cde6a92c5a4b9a733f59","tid":1018752,"uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:09:30.000Z","msg":"私院已經比大陸狗玩到做手術都要排隊<br />\n97前你比到私院價好快到你"},"citedBy":0,